{"tid":1496732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好鬼嘅問卷調查","createTime":"2019-08-22T15:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T19:58:55.000Z","uid":57079,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f91ee459a3e74315cb7720bdad7478dfb75c0eb","tid":1496732,"uid":57079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"話說今個禮拜一  冇喇喇早上十一點幾有錄音打黎話做問卷調查  又係個啲1分極不同意7分極之同意個類  大概係話今次關送送中條例嘅問卷  跟住總共好似有5條問題  <br />\n<br />\n最鬼嘅地方係當我做完第三條之後   佢就話：最後仲有兩條問題  之後佢就分別問咗第一條：「你認唔認為自己係中國人」同埋 第二條：「你認唔認為自己係香港人」<br />\n<br />\n我答晒成份問卷之後先醒起佢冇講自己咩機構  又醒起佢問最尾嗰兩條問題之前嗰句野好似好凝重  彷彿好似喺度警告緊我答得小心啲咁   但大家當然知道我嘅答案係咩啦 當我答完成份問卷之後  佢一句好似快遞騙案嘅音調咁同我講：「拜~拜」令我非常之心寒  <br />\n<br />\n但令我最嬲嘅係：屌你老母多謝都冇句"},{"pid":"b643b35a650844f2f733738f425e0702501c1033","tid":1496732,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:04:03.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒<br />\n<br />\n大家小心"},{"pid":"ae77d02e42398fa31f4215e3c28d449e05837be2","tid":1496732,"uid":57079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"Pish!!<br />\n睇黎大家唔知電話問卷係可以儲低受訪者電話"},{"pid":"7b1fdd661dfe42395aaa40ee4f2f204f205f8fe1","tid":1496732,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">是日（823星期五）活動<br />\n銀髮族罷買<br />\n會計界遊行<br />\n基督徒集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人鏈</span><br />\n賣港城一日遊</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXTv9tG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXTv9tG.png&h=e866629a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span sty